PrecisAppointment of FRANCOISE BERTRAND, of Brossard, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years and designation of FRANCOISE BERTRAND as Chairman of the Canadian Radio- television and Telecommunicatons Commission, effective August 12, 1996.
